This software implements theoretical frameworks from:
- Wolfers & Zitzewitz (2004) - Market efficiency and calibration
- Hanson (2003) - Combinatorial information market design  
- Chen & Pennock (2007) - HARA utility market makers
- Oesterheld et al. (2023) - Performative prediction analysis
- Shapley (1953) - Cooperative game theory
- Pearl (1988) - Probabilistic reasoning
- Brown (1951) - Fictitious play learning

Please cite the original academic papers when using specific theoretical components.
